    <description>If sales event does not have an opportunity tied to the related to field, flow will update related to field with opportunity after an hour of event creation. JH 8/4/23 updated to include gov licensee opps
JH 2/9/24: original build of flow was for when demos were created on close lost accounts and the opp was created after it would associate it an hour after. Flow has been updated to replace PB&quot;Sales Funnel - Set Event WhatID to Open SaaS Opp&quot; and PB triggered flow &quot;Relate Sales Event to Open SaaS Opp&quot; in the run immediate path
06-17-25 - BW - Updated for all Events, not just Sales Events
10-17-2025 - LK - Update to also look for EDU/Assessment opportunity if the Assigned User Role Contains - Upsell Sales Specialist, Education OR Customer Account Specialist, Education. Current issue- when multiple opps are open or still onboarding these EDU task are getting related to the wrong task.</description>
